Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know. I hope you don't mind if I take you to the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a lovely trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're finally on our way to Central now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I nearly forgot. That was quite the detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would be very disingenuous of me not to say well done, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, that's the great thing about working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You make everybody's lives easier and still nobody shows up to wave you goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now. You know everyone at East Headquarters is busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I thought you'd be interested to know that Mr. Glossner character you spent time with has returned to Siam-Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He went back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the man has adamant that he's going to spend the rest of his life there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though civilians aren't allowed on the premises because there's still so much the state wants to look into.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about Crowley again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was. I mean, maybe we're no different than he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we'd taken one wrong step, all of this could have happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you right now, that's one wrong step we're never going to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd never sacrifice life just for our own selfish gains to get an arm or a body that we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrificing somebody's entire life only because you want to be happy, that can never be called equivalent exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just have to keep looking for the real answer out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems that you've grown tremendously through this incident, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown? You mean you really think I got taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
